---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Us - NetWorthCurve.com"
	description="Learn about NetWorthCurve.com's mission to provide privacy-first financial planning tools. Zero tracking, zero cloud sync, complete data sovereignty."
>
	<article class="page-article">
		<div class="page-hero">
			<div class="page-hero-content">
				<span class="page-label">ABOUT US</span>
				<h1 class="page-title">Our Mission: Financial Sovereignty for Everyone</h1>
				<p class="page-lead">NetWorthCurve.com was founded on a simple belief: your financial data belongs to you, and you alone.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="page-content">
			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>Who We Are</h2>
				<p>
                  NetWorthCurve.com is an independent financial technology platform dedicated to building privacy-first financial planning tools that help individuals make smarter financial decisions. Every calculator is designed to be fast, accurate, and completely free to use.
                    </p>
                <p>
                  Unlike many financial platforms that rely on cloud storage or collect sensitive user information, NetWorthCurve performs all calculations entirely within your browser. Your financial data never leaves your device, giving you complete control over your privacy.
                    </p>
           <p>
           Combining modern web technology with security-first design principles, NetWorthCurve aims to make professional-quality financial tools accessible to everyone while maintaining the highest standards of transparency, privacy, and user trust.
              </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block">
    <h2>Meet the Founder</h2>
    <p>
        NetWorthCurve was founded by <strong>Shourya Sai Kammari</strong> who is an <strong>independent developer</strong> with the vision of making powerful financial planning tools accessible while protecting user privacy. My professional background is focused on cybersecurity, security operations, and digital systems integrity.
    </p>
     <p>
        While I don't hold a traditional degree in finance, I have developed a deep personal interest in financial planning and firmly believe that managing personal finances is an essential life skill. Regardless of profession or educational background, understanding money, investing, and long-term wealth creation benefits everyone.
    </p>
     <p>
        That belief inspired me to build NetWorthCurve. The same principles that guide cybersecurity—privacy by design, risk management, accuracy, and system integrity—are embedded throughout this platform. Every calculator runs entirely within your browser without cloud synchronization or unnecessary data collection, ensuring your financial information remains under your control.
    </p>
     <p>
        Beyond developing secure financial tools, I strive to create educational content that simplifies complex financial concepts into practical, data-driven insights. My goal is to help individuals make informed financial decisions while maintaining the highest standards of privacy, transparency, and analytical accuracy.
     </p>
     <p>
        To learn more about my professional background or connect with me directly, visit my
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shourya-sai-kammari-35099a32a/"
           target="_blank"
           rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Personal LinkedIn Profile
            </a>.
             </p>
           </section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2 id="mission">Our Mission</h2>
				<p>We believe that access to powerful financial planning tools should not require surrendering your privacy. Our mission is threefold:</p>
				<ol class="styled-list">
					<li><strong>Empower individuals</strong> with professional-grade financial calculators that rival paid tools in functionality and accuracy.</li>
					<li><strong>Protect user privacy</strong> by eliminating cloud dependency, data collection, and third-party tracking from financial planning.</li>
					<li><strong>Democratize financial literacy</strong> by providing free, accessible educational resources about wealth accumulation and compound interest.</li>
				</ol>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
				<div class="feature-grid">
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
								<path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Zero Data Collection</h3>
						<p>Your financial data never leaves your device. We have no servers storing your net worth, assets, or liabilities. There is nothing to breach because we collect nothing.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Blazing Performance</h3>
						<p>Local calculation eliminates network latency. Every keystroke updates results instantly, providing immediate feedback as you model your financial future.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
								<line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
								<path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Works Offline</h3>
						<p>Without dependency on cloud connectivity, your financial tools work anywhere, anytime. Plane flights, remote locations, or simply choosing to disconnect — our tools remain functional.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="feature-icon">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
								<line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3>No Accounts Required</h3>
						<p>Start calculating immediately. No email addresses, no passwords, no profile creation. Your financial planning session exists only in your browser session.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>Our Values</h2>
				<div class="values-list">
					<div class="value-item">
						<span class="value-number">01</span>
						<div class="value-content">
							<h4>Privacy by Design</h4>
							<p>Every architectural decision prioritizes user privacy. We reject the industry standard of data extraction and instead build systems that safeguard your sovereignty.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="value-item">
						<span class="value-number">02</span>
						<div class="value-content">
							<h4>Accessibility</h4>
							<p>Financial literacy should not be gatekept behind paywalls or require surrendering personal data. Our tools are free to use without subscription or registration.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="value-item">
						<span class="value-number">03</span>
						<div class="value-content">
							<h4>Accuracy</h4>
							<p>Our compound interest and net worth calculations use standard financial formulas employed by professional financial planners. We prioritize mathematical correctness.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="value-item">
						<span class="value-number">04</span>
						<div class="value-content">
							<h4>Transparency</h4>
							<p>Our calculations are visible in client-side JavaScript. No black boxes, no mysterious algorithms. You can inspect exactly how your projections are computed.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block">
				<h2>Disclaimer</h2>
				<p>NetWorthCurve.com provides educational financial tools for informational purposes only. Our calculators are not intended as investment advice, tax guidance, or financial recommendations. The projections generated by our tools are hypothetical scenarios based on user inputs and do not account for all real-world variables.</p>
				<p>Consult with licensed financial advisors, tax professionals, and legal counsel before making significant financial decisions. Past performance does not guarantee future results, and all investments carry risk of loss.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="content-block cta-block">
				<h2>Start Planning Your Financial Future</h2>
				<p>Experience the difference of privacy-first financial tools. No registration, no data collection — just powerful calculations.</p>
				<a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Launch Calculator</a>
			</section>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-article {
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.page-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--charcoal-850) 0%, var(--charcoal-950) 100%);
		padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-4);
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.page-hero::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 600px;
		height: 400px;
		background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.page-hero-content {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.page-label {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--emerald-500);
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.page-lead {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--charcoal-300);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.page-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-4);
	}

	.content-block {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
	}

	.content-block h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
		color: var(--emerald-300);
	}

	.content-block p {
		color: var(--charcoal-200);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.styled-list {
		list-style: decimal;
		padding-left: var(--space-6);
		margin: var(--space-5) 0;
	}

	.styled-list li {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
		color: var(--charcoal-200);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.styled-list strong {
		color: #fff;
	}

	.feature-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: var(--space-5);
		margin-top: var(--space-6);
	}

	.feature-card {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--charcoal-800) 0%, var(--charcoal-850) 100%);
		border: 1px solid var(--charcoal-600);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		padding: var(--space-6);
		transition: all var(--transition-base);
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--emerald-700);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		width: 48px;
		height: 48px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		background: var(--emerald-900);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.feature-icon svg {
		width: 24px;
		height: 24px;
		color: var(--emerald-400);
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}

	.feature-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--charcoal-400);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.values-list {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-5);
	}

	.value-item {
		display: flex;
		gap: var(--space-5);
		padding: var(--space-5);
		background: var(--charcoal-850);
		border: 1px solid var(--charcoal-700);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
	}

	.value-number {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--emerald-600);
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.value-content h4 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
		color: #fff;
	}

	.value-content p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--charcoal-300);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.cta-block {
		text-align: center;
		padding: var(--space-10);
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--emerald-950) 0%, var(--charcoal-950) 100%);
		border: 1px solid var(--emerald-800);
		border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
	}

	.cta-block h2 {
		color: #fff;
	}

	.cta-block p {
		color: var(--charcoal-300);
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.value-item {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: var(--space-3);
		}
	}

	/* Light mode */
	html.light-mode .page-hero { background: #f1f3f5; }
	html.light-mode .page-title { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .page-lead { color: #495057; }
	html.light-mode .content-block h2 { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .content-block p { color: #343a40; }
	html.light-mode .styled-list li { color: #343a40; }
	html.light-mode .styled-list strong { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .feature-card { background: #fff; border-color: #dee2e6; }
	html.light-mode .feature-card:hover { border-color: #16a34a; }
	html.light-mode .feature-card h3 { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .feature-card p { color: #495057; }
	html.light-mode .feature-icon { background: #f0fdf4; }
	html.light-mode .value-item { background: #fff; border-color: #dee2e6; }
	html.light-mode .value-number { color: #16a34a; }
	html.light-mode .value-content h4 { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .value-content p { color: #495057; }
	html.light-mode .cta-block { background: #f0fdf4; border-color: #bbf7d0; }
	html.light-mode .cta-block h2 { color: #101214; }
	html.light-mode .cta-block p { color: #343a40; }
</style>
